    <div class="article-card__content">
        <h3>30 for 30 Challenge: Looking back at the impact</h3>
        <p>In the leadup to World Bipolar Day, our community came together for Bipolar UK’s 30 for 30 Challenge, prioritising their wellbeing while raising an incredible £6,467 for Bipolar UK.</p>
