<a href="/bipolarnews/bipolar-uk-baroness-merron-nhs-hsc-bipolar-friendly-workplace/" class="article-card" title="Continue reading article: 'Bipolar UK responds to Baroness Merron’s World Bipolar Day announcement'">
    <img src="/media/filer_public_thumbnails/filer_public/14/5e/145e4017-3001-40f5-b4c3-a3ba020cf834/news-blog-thumbnails_372x225_1.png__372x225_q80_crop_progressive_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg" alt="">
    <p class="article-meta"><span>30 March 2026</span><span>2 min read</span></p>
    <div class="article-card__content">
        <h3>Bipolar UK responds to Baroness Merron’s World Bipolar Day announcement</h3>
        <p>Baroness Gillian Merron, Minister for Women’s Health and Mental Health, has announced that NHS England and the Department of Health and Social Care are signing up to Bipolar UK’s Bipolar Friendly Workplace Scheme.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="tag-list">
        
